ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectLoran-A Station NF 1984 Termination of Treaty (US) # 11
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to terminate for Canada the EXCHANGE OF NOTES between Canada and the United States of America replacing the Agreement of September 16, 1964, regarding the Construction and Operation and Maintenance of a Loran-C Station in Newfoundland, done on 30 March and 3 May 1984.
